page.title: 17Hobbies
page.content: I go to Gillian Tusan dancing club every Tuesday. We have to take Ballet and Tap shoes and a leotard. If you do gym , modern,tap and ballet it would cost about Â£24 for about six or seven weeks. Every six or seven weeks, we have been we have got another bill to pay. Our teachers name is Gillian Tusan,but we call her Mrs Tusan. I have got six medals for ballet and gym and about eleven certificates for gym, ballet,tap and modern. I like playing squash with my brother. It is played in a room with four walls. First of all you take the feel of the bat. When one person hits the ball against the wall you have to do the same. If you obstruct the other person from hitting the ball it is a point to them.
